    <title>堆排序的简单实现</title>
    <url>/2022/04/15/%E5%A0%86%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<span id="more"></span>

<p>不多说，写给自己看，说实话没有系统地看过算法的书籍，算法导论似乎也不算太好的选择，对于我现在的水平，但是既然看都看了，硬着头皮读。</p>
<p>现在是一刷算法导论，期待明年这个时候回过头看看兴许理解又不一样0.0</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># -*-coding:utf-8-*-</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#堆也叫二叉堆，一种数据结构，堆具有这样一种性质，对堆中任意节点来说，节点的值要么大于等于其子节点的值，要么小于等于其子节点的值。叶子节点没有子节点，是天然的堆</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#为了解决与书上下标起始点不一致的问题，需要修改对书上的伪代码进行细节的修改</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#求下标为i的节点的父节点的下标</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">PARENT</span>(<span class="params">i</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> i&gt;&gt;<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#求下标为i的节点的左孩子节点的下标</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">LEFT</span>(<span class="params">i</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> (i&lt;&lt;<span class="number">1</span>) + <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#求下标为i的节点的右孩子节点的下标</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">RIGHT</span>(<span class="params">i</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> (i&lt;&lt;<span class="number">1</span>)+<span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#使得以下标i为根节点的子树满足最大堆的性质,参数：A，二叉堆，i，下标</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;def MAX_HEAPIFY(A,i):</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    l = LEFT(i)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    r = RIGHT(i)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    #print(&quot;l=&quot;,l)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    if (l &gt;= len(A)): #重点，尽管在python可以不明确return，但这显然不是好的编程习惯，所以我要显示return，再利用python传引用的特性，返回值是数组或者单纯返回都可以</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        print(&quot;返回的A=&quot;,A)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        return A</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    if ( A[l] &gt; A[i]):</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        largest = l</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    else :</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        largest = i</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    #print(&quot;r=&quot;,r)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    if ( r &lt; len(A) and  A[r] &gt; A[largest]):</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        largest = r</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    if (largest != i):</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        A[largest],A[i] = A[i],A[largest]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        #print(&quot;largest=&quot;,largest)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        MAX_HEAPIFY(A,largest)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">MAX_HEAPIFY</span>(<span class="params">A,i</span>): <span class="comment">#</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(<span class="literal">True</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        l = LEFT(i)</span><br><span class="line">        r = RIGHT(i)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(l &lt; <span class="built_in">len</span>(A) <span class="keyword">and</span> A[l] &gt; A[i]):</span><br><span class="line">            largest = l</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            largest = i</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(r &lt; <span class="built_in">len</span>(A) <span class="keyword">and</span> A[r] &gt; A[largest]):</span><br><span class="line">            largest = r</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(largest == i):</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> A</span><br><span class="line">        A[i],A[largest] = A[largest],A[i]</span><br><span class="line">        i = largest</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#有了以上的函数，就可以尝试建立一个最大堆了，将一个以数组形式存储的数据转为二叉堆。参数：数组A。返回值：具有最大堆性质的数组A</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">BUILD_MAX_HEAP</span>(<span class="params">A</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>((<span class="built_in">len</span>(A)-<span class="number">1</span>)//<span class="number">2</span>,-<span class="number">1</span>,-<span class="number">1</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">#print(&quot;i=&quot;,i)</span></span><br><span class="line">        MAX_HEAPIFY(A,i)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> A</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">HEADSORT</span>(<span class="params">A</span>):<span class="comment">#太搞了递归版本的MAX_HEAPIFY的返回值总是空，对递归的细节还有python其实都不够深，好在迭代版本的返回值是有效的</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    length = <span class="built_in">len</span>(A) - <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">    cnt = <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">    BUILD_MAX_HEAP(A)<span class="comment">#构造堆</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;最大堆=&quot;</span>,A)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(length,<span class="number">0</span>,-<span class="number">1</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        A[i],A[<span class="number">0</span>] = A[<span class="number">0</span>],A[i]</span><br><span class="line">        A[:length-cnt] = ( MAX_HEAPIFY(A[:length-cnt],<span class="number">0</span>))</span><br><span class="line">        cnt+=<span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> A</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;A = [16,14,10,8,7,9,3,2,4,1]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">print(HEADSORT(A))#答案是[1, 2, 3, 4, 7, 8, 9, 10, 14, 16]</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">#生成很多随机数，看看堆排序的效果&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> random</span><br><span class="line">A = []</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">10000</span>):<span class="comment">#生成十万个数并排序</span></span><br><span class="line">    A.append(random.randint(<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">10000</span>))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(HEADSORT(A))<span class="comment">#=。= 爆炸了属于是，看起来堆排序在我的计算机上排序10万个数不太行,被迫改成一万，结果1秒不到出了，结果应该是对的</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">B = HEADSORT(A)</span><br><span class="line">C = <span class="built_in">sorted</span>(A)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(B==C)<span class="comment">#True，可以我写的堆排序是正确的！</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
